#: ./docs/10.x/pennant.md:911
#: ./docs/11.x/pennant.md:1027
#: ./docs/master/pennant.md:931
msgctxt "P"
msgid "Laravel does not ship with a directory to contain your extensions. You are free to place them anywhere you like. In this example, we have created an `Extensions` directory to house the `RedisFeatureDriver`."
